Defining Middleware

To create a new middleware, use the make:middleware Artisan command:

	php artisan make:middleware AgeMiddleware

In the structure fo the proyect is in:

proyecto/Http/Middleware

Fro Console to generate middleware
	php artisan make:middleware EdadMiddleware

	Testing our middleware for edad in browser
	OK	
		http://localhost:8000/?edad=19
	Wrong
		http://localhost:8000/?edad=19

		and return in browser
			http://localhost:8000/menordeedad
				"Eres menor de edad"


